      "options": {
        "content": "Tracing samples 5% of new roots by default and honors inbound parent decisions. Enable span export with observability.tracing.enabled. Tempo panels require a Tempo datasource with uid: tempo; the chart auto-provisions it only when observability.tracing.tempo.install and kube-prometheus-stack.install are both true.",
